                "invention-title": [
                    "Process for recovering lithium in waste lithium ion battery",
                    "一种废旧锂离子电池中锂的回收工艺"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of waste battery material recovery, in particular to a process for recovering lithium in a waste lithium ion battery. According to the method, the waste lithium ion battery is discharged and then disassembled, a positive pole piece is crushed and then subjected to high-temperature treatment in a tubular furnace, and a positive pole material and a current collector are separated; immersing the positive electrode material into a sulfuric acid solution containing hydrogen peroxide, adding sufficient calcium carbonate into the filtrate obtained by filtering after the reaction is finished, and filtering out the precipitate separated out by the reaction; and adsorbing lithium ions in the filtrate by using ion exchange resin, washing the adsorption resin by using an acid solution to obtain a lithium-containing solution, and adding sufficient carbonate to react to obtain lithium carbonate. According to the method, the concentration of lithium ions in the leachate is effectively improved, so that the recovery efficiency of lithium is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及废旧电池材料回收技术领域，具体涉及一种废旧锂离子电池中锂的回收工艺。本方法将废旧锂离子电池放电后拆解，正极极片破碎后在管式炉中进行高温处理，分离正极材料和集流体；正极材料浸入到含有双氧水的硫酸溶液中，反应结束后过滤得到的滤液加入足量碳酸钙，滤走反应析出的沉淀；滤液用离子交换树脂吸附滤液中的锂离子，用酸溶液洗涤吸附树脂，得到含锂溶液，加入足量的碳酸盐反应得到碳酸锂。本方法有效提高浸出液中锂离子的浓度，从而提高锂的回收效率。"
                }
            ]
        }
